Name: Adventure Time: Finn and Jake Investigations

Achievements.Name: Home Sweet Home
Achievements.Description: Visit every area in and around the tree house.

Achievements.Name: I See You
Achievements.Description: Use the telescope in the boat to look at three different kingdoms.

Achievements.Name: Snail's Pace
Achievements.Description: Locate and interact with 15 snails.

Achievements.Name: Wrong Number
Achievements.Description: Dial 10 wrong numbers on the pay phone.

Achievements.Name: Radio Starchie
Achievements.Description: Listen to all of the radio broadcasts in the Tree House bedroom.

Achievements.Name: Stretch Goals
Achievements.Description: Use all four Jake combat forms at least once in the game.

Achievements.Name: Combo Time
Achievements.Description: Perform a 15-hit combo in combat without being hit.

Achievements.Name: New to Ooo
Achievements.Description: Say hello to the new character in Ooo.

Achievements.Name: Cake Plate Quest
Achievements.Description: Free Abracadaniel from jail.

Achievements.Name: Wizards Only, Fools
Achievements.Description: Find a way to get into the wizard "party."

Achievements.Name: Sweet, Sweet Magic
Achievements.Description: Defeat the wizards and free the kidnapped Candy People.

Achievements.Name: Hairy Beast
Achievements.Description: Find the hairy beast that has been wreaking havoc.

Achievements.Name: Lump Support
Achievements.Description: Fix all of the noble deeds that were done incorrectly.

Achievements.Name: Long Live The (Ice) King
Achievements.Description: Put the king back in charge of his kingdom.

Achievements.Name: Dance OFF
Achievements.Description: Find a cure for the dancing epidemic.

Achievements.Name: Sound Sword Quest
Achievements.Description: Find the missing Sound Sword.

Achievements.Name: Acceptable Ending
Achievements.Description: Defeat Magic Man's latest jerky plan.

Achievements.Name: Wet Willie
Achievements.Description: Find out why the Fire Kingdom's flames are going out.

Achievements.Name: Cracked
Achievements.Description: Escape from the dungeon below Billy's Cave.

Achievements.Name: Nothung To Lose
Achievements.Description: Find the last of the artifacts and seal Billy's Cave.

Achievements.Name: Record Loss
Achievements.Description: Gather the equipment needed to re-record Finn's record.

Achievements.Name: Band Together
Achievements.Description: Convince Finn's friends to join the band.

Achievements.Name: Real To Reel
Achievements.Description: Put Finn's favorite song back onto the record album.

Achievements.Name: Flimpin' The Diode
Achievements.Description: Correctly guess the Grayble theme.
